<p>
</p>
<h3>
	“stealth”保护壳 by United Nude
</h3>
<p>
	荷兰建筑师 Rem D Koolhaas 创立的英国品牌 United Nude，近期推出了新品“stealth”保护壳，专门放置 12 寸的电子产品。在黑色皮革的外壳上覆盖了一层亚光橡胶涂料，有柔和的光泽和质感。四个边角有立体的处理，显得简洁大方。重要的是它兼有防水防震的功能。售价 149 英镑，<a href="http://www.unitednude.com/stealth-sleeve-black-80-pu-20-cow-leather-2825" target="_blank">这里是购买链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/8fe3fca827b3.jpg" width="818" height="655" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/8f592913c78b.jpg" width="818" height="658" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/25d41602e6b3.jpg" width="818" height="818" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/f2d0da1857c9.jpg" width="818" height="650" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/c85fc592f9c8.jpg" width="818" height="1013" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<h3>
	翻转雨伞 by iumbrella
</h3>
<p>
	这是一把翻转伞，它的伞面是反向的，如果只是稍微淋过雨的雨伞，雨水就完全收在伞里而不会滴出来。它更特别之处在于弯曲的手把可以拆解下来双向安装，因而当雨伞淋过大雨或需要滴水的时候，就可以拆下来装在另一头让它自然滴落。设计者是为了解决雨伞到处滴水，导致地面过去潮湿的问题，这把翻转伞让滴水变得可控。产品目前在众筹，有蓝色和紫色两款，<a href="http://www.zeczec.com/projects/iumbrella" target="_blank">这里是众筹链接。</a> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/db21830eac47.jpg" width="532" height="800" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201510/904a49e76878.jpg" width="590" height="469" title=" " alt=" " /> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
